# Generated artifacts — PDFs are output of build, not source.
# Examples ship as .go programs; running them writes a .pdf next to
# the main.go, which must NOT be committed. The previous
# `!examples/**/*.pdf` exception is gone — there's no good reason
# to track rendered output in a library repo.
/testdata/output/
*.pdf

